13. DATA-AS-UI
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Every displayed item is numbered.
Every number is an actionable command:

[1] Note title → v1 views the note
[2] Subnotebook → v2 opens the subnotebook
[1]/[2]/[3] in path → j2 jumps to position 2
[1]-[5] in search results → v1 views result

No separate controls. No menus. No toolbar.
The data IS the interface. The numbers ARE the commands.
No modes. No hidden states.

